  <thing id="xFreeze" name="Freeze" description="An entombed can drain the heat from a living creature.  On a successful grapple check, the entombed deals 2d4 points of Dexterity damage to a grappled foe (Fortitude save DC 19 half).  This is a supernatural cold effect.  The save DC is Charisma-based." compset="Special" summary="An Entomed deals 2d4 DEX dmg, successful grapple.  Fortitude halves.">
