  <thing id="sDWinIcSto" name="Ice Storm" description="Great magical hailstones pound down for 1 full round, dealing 3d6 points of bludgeoning damage and 2d6 points of cold damage to every creature in the area {b}(a cylinder of 20-ft. radius, 40 ft. high){/b}. A &#150;4 penalty applies to each Listen check made within the {i}ice storm{/i}&#146;s effect, and all land movement within its area is at half speed. At the end of the duration, the hail disappears, leaving no aftereffects (other than the damage dealt).\n\n{i}Arcane Material Component{/i}: A pinch of dust and a few drops of water." compset="Spell" summary="Hail deals 5d6 damage in cylinder 40 ft. across.">
