  <thing id="cFMaPieCol" name="Piercing Cold" description="At 4th level, the frost mage gains Piercing Cold as a bonus metamagic feat. In addition to the normal benefits of the feat, the frost mage bypasses all resistances and immunities to cold granted by spells and spell-like effects of magic items (for example, a {i}ring of minor energy resistance{/i} [cold])." compset="ClSpecial" summary="Gain as a bonus feat.">
