  <thing id="sDrdFrFeSl" name="Frostfell Slide" description="You gain the ability to instantly teleport from one area of slush, snow, or ice to any other area of slush, snow, or ice up to the distance indicated on the table below. Transport distance is based upon the substance touched at the point of departure, not at the point of arrival.\n\nYou may wait to travel in this manner up to the duration of the spell, holding the charge, but immediately upon arriving at the destination point, the spell ends.\n\n{b}Type of Area &#150;&#150; Transport Distance{/b}\nSlush &#150;&#150; 1,000 feet\nSnow &#150;&#150; 2,000 feet\nIce &#150;&#150; 3,000 feet\n\nThe caster must be standing in a frostfell site to cast this spell (to determine if a particular area is considered a frostfell site, see Chapter 1)." compset="Spell" summary="Move instantly from one area of frostfell to another.">
