  <thing id="sSorGelBlo" name="Gelid Blood" description="Cold energy surges through the target&#146;s body, congealing the blood in the creature&#146;s extremities. This effect causes a &#150;4 penalty on attacks, Armor Class, and all Strength- and Dexterity-related checks, and anyone casting a spell with a somatic component has a 50% chance of spell failure for the duration of the spell. If the target makes its Fortitude save, the creature only takes a &#150;2 penalty on attacks, Armor Class, and all Strength- and Dexterity-related checks and has only a 25% chance of spell failure for spells with a somatic component.\n\n{i}Material Component{/i}: A pinch of flour." compset="Spell" summary="Subject takes &#150;4 penalty on attacks, AC, and Str- and Dex-related checks, 50% failure of spells with somatic components.">
