  <thing id="sClrIceSha" name="Ice Shape" description="You can form an existing piece of ice {b}(up to 10 cu. ft. + 1 cu. ft./level){/b} into any shape that suits your purpose. For example, you can make an ice weapon, a special trapdoor, or a crude idol. {i}Ice shape{/i} also permits you to reshape an ice door to make an exit where one didn&#146;t exist or to seal a door shut. While it&#146;s possible to make crude coffers, doors, and so forth with {i}ice shape{/i}, fine detail isn&#146;t possible. There is a 30% chance that any shape including moving parts simply doesn&#146;t work.\n\n{i}Arcane Material Component{/i}: Slush, which must be spread into roughly the desired shape of the ice object and then touched to the ice while the verbal component is uttered." compset="Spell" summary="Sculpts ice into any shape.">
