  <thing id="sWizIceWeb" name="Ice Web" description="{i}Ice web{/i} creates a many-layered mass of strong, frigid strands of pure coldfire. These masses must be anchored to two or more solid and diametrically opposed points&#151;floor and ceiling, opposite walls, or the like&#151;or else the {i}ice web{/i} collapses upon itself and disappears. Creatures caught within the {i}ice web{/i} become entangled in the strands. Attacking a creature in an {i}ice web{/i} won&#146;t cause you to become entangled.\n\nAny creature moving into or through the spell&#146;s area takes 1d6 points of frostburn damage per round.\n\nIn addition, anyone in the effect&#146;s area when the spell is cast must make a Reflex save. If this save succeeds, the creature is entangled, but not prevented from moving, though moving is more difficult than normal (see below). If the save fails, the creature is entangled and can&#146;t move from its space, but can break loose by spending 1 round and making a DC 20 Strength check or a DC 25 Escape Artist check. Once loose (either by making the initial Reflex save or a later Strength check or Escape Artist check), a creature remains entangled, but may move through the {i}ice web{/i} very slowly. Each round devoted to moving allows the creature to make a new Strength check or Escape Artist check. The creature moves 5 feet for each full 5 points by which the check result exceeds 10.\n\nIf you have at least 5 feet of {i}ice web{/i} between you and an opponent, it provides cover. If you have at least 20 feet of {i}ice web{/i} between you, it provides total cover.\n\nThe strands of an {i}ice web{/i} are immune to damage from cold. Any fire&#151;a torch, burning oil, a flaming sword, and so forth&#151;can melt 5 square feet of coldfire strands in 1 round.\n\n{i}Ice web{/i} can be made permanent with a {i}permanency{/i} spell. A permanent ice web that is damaged (but not destroyed) regrows in 10 minutes. Creatures with the cold subtype may pass unimpeded and unharmed through an {i}ice web{/i}.\n\n{i}Coldfire Component{/i}: Two ounces of coldfire. An ounce of coldfire costs 50 gp." compset="Spell" summary="Creates webs of coldfi re that entangle and deal 1d6 frostburn damage/round.">
    <fieldval field="sRange" value="Medium (100 ft. + 10 ft./level)"/>
    <fieldval field="sDuration" value="10 min./level (D)"/>
    <fieldval field="sSave" value="Reflex negates; see text"/>
    <fieldval field="sResist" value="No"/>
    <usesource source="Frostburn"/>
