  <thing id="sSpTFroWea" name="Frost Weapon" description="You imbue a weapon with icy cold, granting it a power similar to the frost special ability. A frost weapon deals an extra 1d6 points of cold damage on a successful hit. If cast on a bow, crossbow, or sling, the spell bestows the cold energy upon the weapon&#146;s ammunition. This ability stacks with the frost special ability, but not with itself.\n\n{i}Material Component{/i}: A drop of water." compset="Spell" summary="Weapon gains frost special ability, +1d6 cold damage.">
