  <thing id="sSpTGlaWar" name="Glacial Ward" description="A faint, shimmering reddish energy encases the subject&#146;s body, granting spell resistance 18 against fire spells and spell-like abilities. In addition, any creature using a fire-based supernatural ability on the subject (such as a breath weapon) must succeed on a DC 18 level check (1d20 + level or HD) to affect a creature warded by this spell.\n\n{i}Material Component{/i}: A pinch of sulfur." compset="Spell" summary="Subject gains SR 18 against fire spells and effects.">
