  <thing id="wIceChuck" name="Icechucker" description="The icechucker appears to be a large crossbow at a casual glance, larger even than a heavy crossbow. Its launching mechanism is designed to fire large shards of ice (usually icicles) rather than regular crossbow bolts. You draw an icechucker back by pulling on a thick lever on the underside of the weapon. Loading an icechucker is a full round action that provokes attacks of opportunity.\n\nIf icicles aren&#146;t handy to load into an icechucker, it can also be used to fire a javelin, dealing the same damage.\n\n{b}Source{/b}: Frostburn" compset="Weapon">
