  <thing id="wIuak" name="Iuak" description="An iuak is a heavily weighted machete-shaped blade, usually made of bone or stone. While it makes an excellent weapon, its primary purpose is to cut through and destroy ice and other hard materials. If used against an object, an iuak ignores the first 3 points of hardness possessed by the object.\n\n{b}Source{/b}: Frostburn" compset="Weapon">
